<li id="cite_note-jbf-74">^ <a href="#cite_ref-jbf_74-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-jbf_74-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFFreeman.2C_Joanne_B1996">Freeman, Joanne B (April 1996 1996). "<a href="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0043-5597%28199604%293%3A53%3A2%3C289%3ADAPRTB%3E2.0.CO%3B2-S" class="external text" title="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0043-5597%28199604%293%3A53%3A2%3C289%3ADAPRTB%3E2.0.CO%3B2-S" rel="nofollow">Dueling as Politics: Reinterpreting the Burr–Hamilton Duel</a>" (subscription). <i>The William and Mary Quarterly, Third Series</i> (Omohundro Institute of Early American History and Culture) <b>53</b> (2): 289–318. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2947402" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2947402" rel="nofollow">10.2307/2947402</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0043-5597%28199604%293%3A53%3A2%3C289%3ADAPRTB%3E2.0.CO%3B2-S" class="external free" title="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0043-5597%28199604%293%3A53%3A2%3C289%3ADAPRTB%3E2.0.CO%3B2-S" rel="nofollow">http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0043-5597%28199604%293%3A53%3A2%3C289%3ADAPRTB%3E2.0.CO%3B2-S</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Dueling+as+Politics%3A+Reinterpreting+the+Burr%E2%80%93Hamilton+Duel&amp;rft.jtitle=The+William+and+Mary+Quarterly%2C+Third+Series&amp;rft.aulast=Freeman%2C+Joanne+B&amp;rft.au=Freeman%2C+Joanne+B&amp;rft.date=April+1996+1996&amp;rft.volume=53&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=289%E2%80%93318&amp;rft.pub=Omohundro+Institute+of+Early+American+History+and+Culture&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F2947402&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flinks.jstor.org%2Fsici%3Fsici%3D0043-5597%2528199604%25293%253A53%253A2%253C289%253ADAPRTB%253E2.0.CO%253B2-S&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexander_Hamilton"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
