<li id="cite_note-82"><b><a href="#cite_ref-82" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.nps.gov/hagr/" class="external text" title="http://www.nps.gov/hagr/" rel="nofollow">"Hamilton Grange National Memorial (U.S. National Park Service)"</a>. Nps.gov<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nps.gov/hagr/" class="external free" title="http://www.nps.gov/hagr/" rel="nofollow">http://www.nps.gov/hagr/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-03-14</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Hamilton+Grange+National+Memorial+%28U.S.+National+Park+Service%29&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Nps.gov&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nps.gov%2Fhagr%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexander_Hamilton"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
